                <li>7-day free trial with no credit card</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>AI Agent output needs editing — better for research than drafting</li>
                <li>Lifetime-deal users were moved to a limited legacy tier</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-foot">
            <div class="tool-best-for"><strong>Best for:</strong> Strategists who want SERP-backed briefs before writing.</div>
            <a href="/reviews/frase/" class="tool-cta-btn">Read review →</a>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="tool-card">
          <div class="tool-card-head">
            <div class="tool-rank">05</div>
            <div class="tool-card-info">
              <div class="tool-card-name">Writesonic</div>
              <div class="tool-card-tag">Best all-in-one AI writing</div>
            </div>
            <div class="tool-card-price">
