              <div class="per">Individual plan</div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="tool-card-body">
            <div>
              <h5>What it does better</h5>
              <ul class="yes-list">
                <li>Free tier — broader than Junia's restricted free plan</li>
                <li>WordPress auto-publish + built-in image generation</li>
                <li>100+ templates and 25+ languages</li>
              </ul>
            </div>
            <div>
              <h5>Trade-offs</h5>
              <ul class="no-list">
                <li>Credit system makes monthly cost unpredictable</li>
                <li>SEO optimization is shallow vs Surfer or Frase</li>
