              <span class="time">10 min</span>
              <h4>Inventory your top 50 ranking pages</h4>
              <p>Open Plausible or Search Console and sort by clicks over 90 days. Flag pages that need refreshes — these go first in your new tool.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="migration-step">
            <div>
              <span class="time">20 min</span>
              <h4>Recreate brand voice in the new tool</h4>
              <p>theStacc, Jasper, and Scalenut accept brand voice via URL or pasted text. Drop in your 3 best-performing posts — usually faster than rebuilding a Junia voice profile.</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="migration-step">
            <div>
              <span class="time">60 min</span>
              <h4>Connect your CMS</h4>
